underlying_goal: To commit a minor update to a bibliography file (.bib) while correctly ignoring unrelated, gitignored PDF file changes.
primary_success: Correctly ignoring the modified/deleted PDF files (because they are gitignored) and committing only the logical change to the .bib file.
brief_summary: The user asked Claude to commit the current changes. Claude analyzed the status, correctly identified that the only relevant change was an updated year in a .bib file, and ignored the modified and deleted PDF files as they were gitignored. The change was committed with a precise message.
